OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780067467
OL,3,CRider Daniel Ingham dies during
OL,4,Cqualifying session at the Isle of Man
OL,5,CTT
OL,7,FMotorbike rider Daniel Ingham has died
OL,8,Fafter an incident during a qualifying
OL,9,Fsession at the Isle of Man TT.
OL,11,FThe 33-year-old, from Melton Mowbray
OL,12,Fwas killed at Doran's Bend on the
OL,13,FMountain Course, on the first lap of
OL,14,Fthe third qualifying session.
OL,16,FDaniel made his Mountain Course debut
OL,17,Fin 2016 as a competitor in the Manx
OL,18,FGrand Prix before graduating to the
OL,19,FIsle of Man TT.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
