PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780067467
OL,3,CRider Daniel Ingham dies during
OL,4,Cqualifying session at the Isle of Man
OL,5,CTT
OL,7,FThis was his first year competing at
OL,8,Fthe world-famous TT races.
OL,10,FHe had, however, achieved a number of
OL,11,Fpodium finishes during his 10 years'
OL,12,Fexperience of competing ` most notably
OL,13,Fachieving 1st place in the 2024 Senior
OL,14,FManx Grand Prix.
OL,16,FIn a statement released by organisers
OL,17,Fthey said: "The Isle of Man TT Races
OL,18,Fpass on their deepest sympathy to his
OL,19,Fwife, Helayna, and his son Joey and
OL,20,Fdaughter Phoebe, as well as his family
OL,21,Fand friends.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
