OL,3,CRider Daniel Ingham dies during
OL,4,Cqualifying session at the Isle of Man
OL,5,CTT
OL,7,F"A popular and well-respected member
OL,8,Fof the road racing community, Daniel's
OL,9,Fpassion for the sport was evident to
OL,10,Fall who knew him."
